{"tid":1029061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"銃夢：戰鬥天使機械臂成真　電影團隊3D 打印 Alita 義肢贈英國少女","createTime":"2019-02-20T03:18:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-20T07:29:44.000Z","uid":184679,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"07ddc17bd534200d75329791428521cd0b5c7a95","tid":1029061,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T03:18:04.000Z","msg":"銃夢：戰鬥天使由漫畫改篇成荷里活大電影，女主角 Alita（漫畫版加里 Gally）先後使用了兩套機械身軀。現實中的英國少女 Tilly 因為年幻時的疾病而截肢，銃夢的電影製作團體就特別聯同 Open Bionics，以 3D 打印技術，為 Tilly 製作跟 Alita 狂戰士設計相同的義肢。<br />\n<br />\n以《銃夢：戰鬥天使》Alita 狂戰士模式的外型設計作為參考的這一對義肢，其實是《銃夢》電影製作團體，與專門製作義肢的 Open Bionics 合作設計。而現年 13 歲的 Tilly Lockey，在 15 個月大的時候因為腦膜炎併發敗血病（Meningococcal Septicaemia Strain B），必須將一雙手截肢。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2444663/org/5e0c649745967589e55c350a6bb612e9.jpg/zzMkV5lopnUmPzqvq3Q4VLI4pBcu69ZruPu4Pbj7uD0?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2444663%2Forg%2F5e0c649745967589e55c350a6bb612e9.jpg%2FzzMkV5lopnUmPzqvq3Q4VLI4pBcu69ZruPu4Pbj7uD0%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=92855a11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nTi<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">lly 戴上由 Open Bionics 開發跟 Alita 設計相同的 Hero Arm 義肢，與 Alita 演員 Rosa Salazar 在《銃夢：戰鬥天使》的英國首映中合照。（20th Century Fox）</span><br />\n<br />\nTilly 成長過程中多次更換不同的義肢以配合身體的成長，而這些義肢基本上都是價格昂貴卻功能不多；今次由 Open Bionics 開發的 Hero Arm 義肢，就是以 3D 打印技術配合全新的各種醫學感應器材，令製作成本大幅下降，而且義肢的手指有更大的靈活度，可以做到更多先前義肢不可能做到的動作。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2444659/org/e452d1ddb1c46f13218544cef972eacc.jpg/RAXnTW-MvySVDistNg7e-fttRsFLkl3IQiT3gUIk94E\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2444659%2Forg%2Fe452d1ddb1c46f13218544cef972eacc.jpg%2FRAXnTW-MvySVDistNg7e-fttRsFLkl3IQiT3gUIk94E&h=df37e96f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2444681/org/6e6fead678355a74b9a0c50886422a78.jpg/Le3b_4_UiPtDFmi1jOMS779yyHmKXGWE1GUb89RlG_M\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2444681%2Forg%2F6e6fead678355a74b9a0c50886422a78.jpg%2FLe3b_4_UiPtDFmi1jOMS779yyHmKXGWE1GUb89RlG_M&h=61b17ad6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2444684/org/3f3cfadb3a7b9e1262896afa59eea65d.jpg/O5FjpmFnMs-GJMi1eQ-y1tDG2LxEEZCetZLaM7WS2jM\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2444684%2Forg%2F3f3cfadb3a7b9e1262896afa59eea65d.jpg%2FO5FjpmFnMs-GJMi1eQ-y1tDG2LxEEZCetZLaM7WS2jM&h=b61f7144&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nTilly 獲贈這一對狂戰士模式的 Hero Arm，更參與《銃夢：戰鬥天使》的英國首映，與飾演 Alita 的 Rosa Salazar 合照。Tilly 在使用 Hero Arm 之後，可以更容易去撿起物件，例如在 Wii 上進行《Just Dance》遊戲時，她需要以膠布將 Wii Remote 貼在手上，而使用 Hero Arm 之後，就可以自己拿起 Wii Remote 進行遊戲。大家可以從以下影片中，見到 Tilly 在佩戴 Hero Arm 之後，動作非常靈活。<br />\n<br />\n其實 Open Bionics 已經在官網推出 Hero Arm 的各款外殼，至於實際有需要安裝 Hero Arm 的朋友，就需要透過職業治療師聯絡 Open Bionics 去訂製。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2444689/org/809834c01823771480413a776a903db7.jpg/7GyP6_Y-0OQsJ20MrwPjDpJKUYER2Wr6WFqOf1hajn8?v=w1600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2444689%2Forg%2F809834c01823771480413a776a903db7.jpg%2F7GyP6_Y-0OQsJ20MrwPjDpJKUYER2Wr6WFqOf1hajn8%3Fv%3Dw1600&h=5295be32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">Open Bionics 官網上，已經有多款 Hero Arm 的外殼可以選擇。（Open Bionics）</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GNnFNxx4Exw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DGNnFNxx4Exw&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n87P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=ea01df43\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=GNnFNxx4Exw</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/295558/%E9%8A%83%E5%A4%A2-%E6%88%B0%E9%AC%A5%E5%A4%A9%E4%BD%BF%E6%A9%9F%E6%A2%B0%E8%87%82%E6%88%90%E7%9C%9F-3d-%E6%89%93%E5%8D%B0-alita-%E7%BE%A9%E8%82%A2%E8%B4%88%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3#media_id=2444684\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2595%25B8%25E7%25A2%25BC%25E7%2594%259F%25E6%25B4%25BB%2F295558%2F%25E9%258A%2583%25E5%25A4%25A2-%25E6%2588%25B0%25E9%25AC%25A5%25E5%25A4%25A9%25E4%25BD%25BF%25E6%25A9%259F%25E6%25A2%25B0%25E8%2587%2582%25E6%2588%2590%25E7%259C%259F-3d-%25E6%2589%2593%25E5%258D%25B0-alita-%25E7%25BE%25A9%25E8%2582%25A2%25E8%25B4%2588%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25B0%2591%25E5%25A5%25B3%23media_id%3D2444684&d=WIvcVJ42Qixy%2BOT8%2FM1n87P2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=5b645828\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E7%94%9F%E6%B4%BB/295558/%E9%8A%83%E5%A4%A2-%E6%88%B0%E9%AC%A5%E5%A4%A9%E4%BD%BF%E6%A9%9F%E6%A2%B0%E8%87%82%E6%88%90%E7%9C%9F-3d-%E6%89%93%E5%8D%B0-alita-%E7%BE%A9%E8%82%A2%E8%B4%88%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%91%E5%A5%B3#media_id=2444684</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2270000/2273867/Tilly-background-1_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2270000%2F2273867%2FTilly-background-1_1024.jpg&h=2144b061&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d10bd98319c8c6fc1740f477139e9f27aaa5f6be","tid":1029061,"uid":220431,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T03:37:19.000Z","msg":"開始練火星機甲術"},{"pid":"8a08f40305a926548232f4397fcdc3456aa43a16","tid":1029061,"uid":104078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T04:28:10.000Z","msg":"俾佢伏打點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0313594c21e50e547c638c81c1ceadc5e4c2dc07","tid":1029061,"uid":28435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-20T04:29:44.000Z","msg":"warrior hunter <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal